  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\n`forge 0.2.0 (ae3ec74 2023-08-26T00:16:39.244732249Z)`\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge test\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nMy `forge` test time increased over the last week almost by 20mins _without_ making changes in the contract or test code: \r\n![image](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/assets/25297591/a3c70aaa-8117-42d7-bf4b-93edee38f3d7)\r\n\r\nYou can replicate the behaviour [here](https://github.com/pcaversaccio/snekmate/actions/workflows/test-contracts.yml).",
